                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-12-defend144 t18000115-12-punish63"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18000115-12-punish64" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000115-12-punish64" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000115-12-punish64" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-12-defend142 t18000115-12-punish64"></join>
               fined 1s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Forsman <rs id="t18000115-12-verdict65" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000115-12-verdict65" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice LAWRENCE.</p>
